{
  "script_id": "divergence-curl",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "想象一阵风吹过平原，每一点都有一个方向和快慢。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "把每点的风画成一支箭头，就得到一个向量场。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "我们想问：这片风是在往外喷，还是在打旋？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "divergence",
      "line_id": "div-1",
      "filename": "divergence-div-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/divergence-div-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "散度衡量一点是往外发散还是向内汇聚。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "divergence",
      "line_id": "div-2",
      "filename": "divergence-div-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/divergence-div-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "散度为正，箭头向四周射出，这里像个源，我们标成红色。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "divergence",
      "line_id": "div-3",
      "filename": "divergence-div-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/divergence-div-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "散度为负，箭头向中心涌入，这里像个汇，标成蓝色。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "curl",
      "line_id": "curl-1",
      "filename": "curl-curl-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/curl-curl-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.51,
      "size": 24192,
      "text": "旋度衡量一点附近的流动有多爱打转。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "curl",
      "line_id": "curl-2",
      "filename": "curl-curl-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/curl-curl-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "旋度为正是逆时针涡旋，为负则是顺时针。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "curl",
      "line_id": "curl-3",
      "filename": "curl-curl-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/curl-curl-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "放一片小叶子进去，它自转的快慢就是旋度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "fields",
      "line_id": "field-1",
      "filename": "fields-field-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/fields-field-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "源场只发散不打转，散度正而旋度为零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "fields",
      "line_id": "field-2",
      "filename": "fields-field-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/fields-field-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "旋转场只打转不发散，旋度不零而散度为零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "fields",
      "line_id": "field-3",
      "filename": "fields-field-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/fields-field-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "剪切场看似平直，却藏着一份隐蔽的旋度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "切换不同的场，观察标注点的散度与旋度如何变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "加密网格，箭头越细就越能看清流动的走向。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "散度看源与汇，旋度看涡旋，两者刻画向量场的本质。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divergence-curl/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "它们是电磁、流体等物理定律的通用语言。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divergence-curl",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
